he types of vehicles you could drive were known as ‘groups’. These are now known as ‘categories’.</p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>You can <a href=\"/exchange-paper-driving-licence-photocard-licence\" title=\"Exchange your paper driving licence for a photocard licence\">exchange your paper driving licence for a new photocard licence</a>.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Licences issued between 1976 and 1986</h2>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Group</th>\n      <th>Vehicles you can drive</th>\n      <th>Driving licence category after 1997</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>A</td>\n      <td>Car or light vehicle up to 3,500 kilograms (<abbr title=\"kilograms\">kg</abbr>) Maximum Authorised Mass (<abbr title=\"Maximum Authorised Mass\">MAM</abbr>)</td>\n      <td>B</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>A</td>\n      <td>Medium-sized vehicle between 3,500 and 7,500kg <abbr title=\"Maximum Authorised Mass\">MAM</abbr></td>\n      <td>C1</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>A</td>\n      <td>Vehicles between 3,500 and 7,500kg <abbr title=\"Maximum Authorised Mass\">MAM</abbr> with a trailer (combined weight no more than 8,250kg <abbr title=\"Maximum Authorised Mass\">MAM</abbr>)</td>\n      <td>C1E (with <a href=\"/driving-licence-codes\" title=\"Driving licence codes\">restriction code 79 or 107</a>)</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>A</td>\n      <td>Minibus with 9 to 16 passenger seats (not driving for ‘hire or reward’)</td>\n      <td>D1 (with <a href=\"/driving-licence-codes\" title=\"Driving licence codes\">restriction code 79 or 101</a>)</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>A</td>\n      <td>Vehicles in groups B, C, E, F, K, L and N below</td>\n      <td>See below</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>B</td>\n      <td>Group A vehicles (automatic only)</td>\n      <td>Above categories (with <a href=\"/driving-licence-codes\" title=\"Driving licence codes\">restriction code 78</a>)</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td