fter an accident</td>\n      <td>5 to 10</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>AC20</td>\n      <td>Failing to give particulars or report an accident within 24 hours</td>\n      <td>5 to 10</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>AC30</td>\n      <td>Undefined accident offences</td>\n      <td>4 to 9</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Disqualified driver</h2>\n<p>These codes must stay on a driving licence for 4 years from the date of the offence.</p>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Code</th>\n      <th>Offence</th>\n      <th>Penalty points</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>BA10</td>\n      <td>Driving while disqualified by order of court</td>\n      <td>6</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>BA30</td>\n      <td>Attempting to drive while disqualified by order of court</td>\n      <td>6</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Careless driving</h2>\n\n<p>Codes CD10 to CD30 must stay on a driving licence for 4 years from the date of the offence.</p>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Code</th>\n      <th>Offence</th>\n      <th>Penalty points</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>CD10</td>\n      <td>Driving without due care and attention</td>\n      <td>3 to 9</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>CD20</td>\n      <td>Driving without reasonable consideration for other road users</td>\n      <td>3 to 9</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>CD30</td>\n      <td>Driving without due care and attention or without reasonable consideration for other road users</td>\n      <td>3 to 9</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>Codes CD40 to CD70 must stay on a driving licence for 11 years from the date of the conviction.</p>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Code</th>\n      <th>Offence</th>\n      <th>Penalty points</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>CD40</td>\n      <td>Causing death through careless driving when unfit through drink</td>\n      <td>3 to 11</td>\n  